<html>

<head>
	<title>Reservation Confirmation</title>
	<style type="text/css">
	div.reservationCard {
		background-color: #eeeeaa;
		color: #000000;
		padding: 1em;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	
	div.reservationCard h2 {
		font-family: Palatino, serif;
		font-style: italic;
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 0px;
		font-size: 200%;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	div.reservationContainer {
		width: 50%;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	div.reservationContainer input {
		width: 100%;
		height: 3em;
		color: white;
		font-weight: bold;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		font-size: 1em;
		font-weight: bold;
		border: 3px outset black;
		cursor: pointer;
	}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<p>Hi there <%=h @reservation.session.topic.name %> instructors,</p>

<p><%=h @reservation.user.name %>, one of the students in your upcoming 
	"<%=h @reservation.session.topic.name %>" class on <%=h formatted_time_range(@reservation.session.time, @reservation.session.topic.minutes) %>, has requested special
	accommodations for his/her needs:</p>
	
<%- if @reservation.special_accommodations.blank? -%>
  <p>&lt; None. The student has deleted his previous request. &gt;</p>
<%- else -%>
  <p><%=h @reservation.special_accommodations %></p>
<%- end -%>

<p>If you have any questions about this request, you can reach 
	<%=h @reservation.user.name %> at 
	<a href="mailto:<%=h @reservation.user.email %>"><%=h @reservation.user.email %></a>.
	</p>

</body>

</html>

